message.body: Am I meeting you at your apartment? I'm trying to decide the best way to get down there, and whether I should bring the printer along.

The printer would be good, if you want to drive down theres an exit off 76 pretty close to my house and parking isnt that bad. Or if you take the train in we can meet in center city, ill be at school in the merriam thatre until 6
I missed my train! I will have to catch a later one.
I'm on the 5:48; I will arrive at Suburban at 6:45.
Ok, ill meet you at suburban then
